{"tid":1946872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"妻兒與空凳合照 倒數王全璋出獄","createTime":"2020-03-28T02:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T02:35:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe0274dcd49d0c0d25e47968a7a912ae77c2536","tid":1946872,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200328/CYQH6DDEMLH2PJDJDOS43CEXAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200328%2FCYQH6DDEMLH2PJDJDOS43CEXAA%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=2151af98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200328%2FCYQH6DDEMLH2PJDJDOS43CEXAA%2F&h=accdef54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200328/CYQH6DDEMLH2PJDJDOS43CEXAA/</a><br />\n<br />\n妻兒與空凳合照 倒數王全璋出獄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200328/large/1585324616_15da.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200328%2Flarge%2F1585324616_15da.gif&h=77852516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李文足和兒子隔着空凳而坐，中間座位貼上王全璋（右圖）的畫像，期待他獲釋團聚。<br />\n<br />\n內地709案最後一人、維權律師王全璋涉嫌煽動顛覆國家政權罪判囚四年半，前日是他刑滿獲釋倒數第10天。妻子李文足發佈短片，她和兒子隔着空凳而坐，中間座位貼上王全璋的畫像，期待丈夫獲釋。她警告，一旦丈夫出獄後，卻不能回到北京和家人團聚，她將繼續抗爭，直至王全璋回復真正的自由。<br />\n<br />\n「不能團聚將繼續抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n該段名為「王全璋回家倒計時──10天」的短片，可見李文足和兒子泉泉先隔空凳而坐，中間座位貼上相信是兒子親繪的王全璋畫像；畫面之後一轉，兒子改坐在中間，雙手一邊搭着母親，一邊搭着貼上父親王全璋畫像的座椅，母子倆展露微笑，期待王全璋歸來。李文足表示，有人擔心王全璋下月5日獲釋，但未得到真正的自由，未必能回京和家人一同生活，但她早有思想準備：「有人擔心王全璋在4月5日不能回到北京，跟一家人團聚。如果要繼續控制王全璋、軟禁他，或是把他弄到別的地方，我也做好了思想準備，那我會繼續去司法部、公安部等機構繼續控告，直至王全璋回復真正的自由，回到北京跟我們團聚。」王全璋日前致函李文足，透露他獲釋後或遭當局軟禁在戶籍地山東濟南。<br />\n<br />\n李文足表示，她上周六發出第一條倒數短片後，收到各地傳來的祝福，覺得相當感動：「倒計時的日子對我來說真的是特別煎熬，但是當我看到那麼多的人關注、支持着我們、給我打氣，送上了滿滿的祝福，我被感動、被安慰、被鼓勵。」現年44歲的王全璋2015年7月被當局帶走，法院去年1月宣判，王涉「顛覆國家政權罪」判囚四年半，扣減被羈留的三年多時間，將於下月初出獄。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter"},{"pid":"e35d55705dc81c925095b3597330cd6c73c97d6b","tid":1946872,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"318c5551ef528f8a0776a91dab0176d43a78aafc","tid":1946872,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:05:45.000Z","msg":"走左先開心啦<br />\n而家先最危險<br />\n唔死都變傻"},{"pid":"7c05664aa147d5e5d1910436837841908bf00dbc","tid":1946872,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"應該同江天勇一樣 出獄就失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc9bbf916d1bda16b4ae6ba3faaaa90d747dea0","tid":1946872,"uid":165199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c05664aa147d5e5d1910436837841908bf00dbc","tid":1946872,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"應該同江天勇一樣 出獄就失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"或者已經比人整傻左...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d096e1c2eaf3cb63b3b28487e92497b5ec2ecf1","tid":1946872,"uid":137506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2dc9bbf916d1bda16b4ae6ba3faaaa90d747dea0","tid":1946872,"uid":165199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c05664aa147d5e5d1910436837841908bf00dbc","tid":1946872,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"應該同江天勇一樣 出獄就失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"或者已經比人整傻左...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"江天勇係獄入面俾人逼食不知明藥物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金變玲本身想接江天勇去美國全家團聚 點知江天勇一出監就俾國安接走 話俾個新環境新工作佢生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家都冇人知佢去左邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243a3def150d752b687056c77dcdf3bb6b5886dd","tid":1946872,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:35:54.000Z","msg":"我以為邊撚個叫倒數王<br />\n倒數都有王咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}